### Delivery Challan API Tests

@baseURL = http://localhost:5000/api
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create a new delivery challan
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "676b8f8e12345678901234567",
  "date": "2025-01-31",
  "taxType": "exclusive",
  "discountType": "flat",
  "discountValue": 100,
  "shipping": 50,
  "roundOff": true,
  "showHSN": true,
  "showUnit": true,
  "showSignature": false,
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Product A",
      "hsn": "1001",
      "unit": "PCS",
      "quantity": 10,
      "rate": 100,
      "discount": 5,
      "discountType": "flat",
      "taxType": "cgst_sgst",
      "taxRate": 18
    },
    {
      "name": "Product B",
      "hsn": "1002",
      "unit": "KG",
      "quantity": 5,
      "rate": 200,
      "discount": 10,
      "discountType": "percentage",
      "taxType": "igst",
      "taxRate": 12
    }
  ],
  "terms": "Delivery within 7 days",
  "notes": "Handle with care",
  "status": "draft"
}

### 2. Get all delivery challans with pagination
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans?page=1&limit=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 3. Get delivery challan by ID
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/676b8f8e12345678901234567
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Update delivery challan
PUT {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/676b8f8e12345678901234567
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Updated notes - urgent delivery",
  "shipping": 75,
  "status": "draft"
}

### 5. Update delivery challan status
PATCH {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/676b8f8e12345678901234567/status
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "sent"
}

### 6. Preview delivery challan number
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/preview-number
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 7. Search delivery challans
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/search?search=Product&status=draft&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 8. Get delivery challan statistics
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/stats?period=30
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 9. Duplicate delivery challan
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/676b8f8e12345678901234567/duplicate
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 10. Create delivery challan from quotation
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/from-quotation/676b8f8e12345678901234567
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-01-31",
  "notes": "Created from quotation"
}

### 11. Convert delivery challan to invoice
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/676b8f8e12345678901234567/convert-to-invoice
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceTitle": "Invoice for Delivery",
  "dueDate": "2025-02-15",
  "notes": "Payment due on delivery",
  "terms": "Net 15 days"
}

### 12. Bulk actions - Mark as delivered
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/bulk-actions
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "mark_delivered",
  "deliveryChallanIds": [
    "676b8f8e12345678901234567",
    "676b8f8e12345678901234568"
  ]
}

### 13. Bulk actions - Send delivery challans
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/bulk-actions
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "send",
  "deliveryChallanIds": [
    "676b8f8e12345678901234567",
    "676b8f8e12345678901234568"
  ]
}

### 14. Bulk actions - Delete delivery challans
POST {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/bulk-actions
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "delete",
  "deliveryChallanIds": [
    "676b8f8e12345678901234567"
  ]
}

### 15. Delete delivery challan
DELETE {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/676b8f8e12345678901234567
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 16. Filter by status
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans?status=delivered&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 17. Filter by client
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans?clientId=676b8f8e12345678901234567&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 18. Filter by date range
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans?dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-01-31&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 19. Filter converted to invoice
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans?convertedToInvoice=false&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 20. Complex search with multiple filters
GET {{baseURL}}/finance/sales/delivery-challans/search?search=urgent&status=sent&clientId=676b8f8e12345678901234567&dateFrom=2025-01-01&convertedToInvoice=false&sortBy=date&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}
